-- multiSearchAny with more than 255 needles raises an exception, with and without the index
-- 255 needles is accepted by the index
0
-- valid multiSearchAny uses the index and returns the matching rows
2
-- multiMatchAny with allow_hyperscan = 0 raises an exception, with and without the index
-- multiMatchAny with a regexp longer than max_hyperscan_regexp_length raises an exception, with and without the index
-- multiMatchAny with an expensive regexp raises an exception when reject_expensive_hyperscan_regexps = 1, with and without the index
-- the same expensive regexp is accepted when reject_expensive_hyperscan_regexps = 0
0
-- multiMatchAny with a regexp Hyperscan cannot compile raises an exception, with and without the index
-- the same applies when only one needle in the set is malformed
-- valid multiMatchAny uses the index and returns the matching rows
1
